OL,3,CNewcastle United hero Dan Burn 'waited
OL,4,Ca long time' for England call-up
OL,6,FHaving come straight from Wembley
OL,7,Fafter helping Newcastle beat
OL,8,FLiverpool, it was a whirlwind 24 hours
OL,9,Ffor Dan Burn.
OL,11,FThe defender arrived for training with
OL,12,FThomas Tuchel's new squad on Tuesday
OL,13,Fas they prepare to face Albania in a
OL,14,FWorld Cup qualifier on Friday.
OL,16,F"As soon as we left the stadium, my
OL,17,Ffocus had fully switched to this," he
OL,18,Fsaid at a press conference at St.
OL,19,FGeorge's Park on Tuesday.
