OL,6,FBut Burn brushed off that criticism,
OL,7,Fsaying: "I don't think it really
OL,8,Fmatters. It is not the first time
OL,9,Fwe've had a manager from another
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,F"If he's the most qualified and can
OL,13,Fhelp us win a World Cup, I don't think
OL,14,Fit really matters"
OL,16,FOther call-ups
OL,18,FArsenal's Miles Lewis-Skelly, 18, and
OL,19,FJarrell Quansah, 22, will both hope to
OL,20,Fmake their senior England debuts in
OL,21,FWorld Cup qualifiers at Wembley.
