OL,6,FMarcus Rashford and Jordan Henderson
OL,7,Fare other headline names in Tuchel's
OL,8,Ffirst squad.
OL,10,FFormer Liverpool captain Jordan
OL,11,FHenderson is also back. The Ajax
OL,12,Fmidfielder's last appearance for the
OL,13,FThree Lions was in November 2023
OL,14,Fagainst Malta.
OL,16,FRashford was frozen out by new
OL,17,FManchester United head coach Ruben
OL,18,FAmorim in December but he has
OL,19,Fimpressed since joining Aston Villa on
OL,20,Floan in January.
